fields.content: Absolutely captivating story with a truly immersive cyberpunk atmosphere. The choice-based narrative feels meaningful, with decisions that significantly impact the story's direction. The protagonist's struggle against corporate control feels timely and relevant.

As a fantasy writer myself, I'm deeply impressed by the world-building in this story. The magical system feels fresh and original, while still drawing on classic fantasy elements. Looking forward to seeing where the narrative goes!

A brilliantly crafted mystery with an engaging protagonist. The historical elements are well-researched, and the cipher at the center of the plot is genuinely intriguing. My only critique is that some of the academic politics feels a bit clich√©.

The technical aspects of this story are impressively accurate for science fiction. The neural interface concepts feel plausible and well-thought-out. The interactive elements add an engaging layer to what might otherwise be a fairly standard cyberpunk narrative.

This guide is incredibly practical and accessible for writers who, like me, don't have a strong technical background. The step-by-step instructions for setting up a basic author website answered questions I didn't even know I had. Highly recommended resource!
